1.0.name: wordpress/simple-site-valuation
1.0.description: By using this plugin you'll be creating a badge that will display your domain's current estimated value in dollars, Google page rank, and Alexa popularity ... usefull for small seo campaigns. These key seo values or simply the site valuation will convince your visitors of the work amount you've put onto your domain. Once created, the image badge (.png) will self update when your seo page report at domof.com will be updated.
